Project (1)
Integrative taxonomy, systematics and evolution of darkling beetles
Project
Characterization of species complexes using ecological, morphological and molecular data. Higher level systematics of darkling beetles. Unravelling diversification dynamics of focal tenebrionid clades with a focus on species from the Mediterranean basin and New Caledonia. Investigating the impact on past climate changes on darkling beetle lineages.
